image_analysis.description: A high-angle interior photograph of a formal library or study. The room features orange-red walls with white ornate crown molding and a large white built-in bookcase filled with numerous books. In front of the bookcase is a teal velvet tufted sofa with a green patterned throw pillow. To the left is a white armchair with black trim and a gold-based lamp with a pleated shade. In the foreground, there is a white rectangular ottoman with gold stud detailing and a dark wood tray on top. The floor is covered by a large rug with yellow, teal, and black abstract patterns. Two telescopes are mounted on top of the bookcase.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room setting with furniture in the foreground and midground, and a large bookcase against the back wall.
